   abs_error |      2,029    11160.98     26167.8          0   507848.8

. 
. * Correlation between actual wage and predicted wage
. corr WAGP wage_hat
(obs=2,029)

             |     WAGP wage_hat
-------------+------------------
        WAGP |   1.0000
    wage_hat |   0.9403   1.0000


. 
. * Export prediction output
. export delimited using processed_data/ps5_prediction_output.csv, replace
file processed_data/ps5_prediction_output.csv saved

